# Pine Script v6 — Cursor Rules
# Maintainer: Ugur Pala · mail@ugurpala.com · github.com/trugurpala/pinescriptv6

---

## TR | Protokol

Kod yazmadan önce:
1. `LESSONS_LEARNED.md` oku — bilinen hatalar burada
2. `LLM_MANIFEST.md` ile göreve uygun dosyayı bul
3. O dosyayı oku, sonra kodu yaz
4. Hata olunca: çöz + `LESSONS_LEARNED.md`'ye ekle

## EN | Protocol

Before writing code:
1. Read `LESSONS_LEARNED.md` — known errors are there
2. Use `LLM_MANIFEST.md` to find the correct file
3. Read that file, then write the code
4. On error: solve + append to `LESSONS_LEARNED.md`

---

## Kesin Kurallar / Non-Negotiable Rules

```pine
//@version=6   // her scriptin ilk satırı / first line of EVERY script
```

| ❌ v5 — Kullanma | ✅ v6 — Kullan |
|-----------------|---------------|
| `study("name")` | `indicator("name")` |
| `security(ticker, tf, expr)` | `request.security(ticker, tf, expr)` |
| `input(14, type=input.integer)` | `input.int(14, "Label")` |
| `array.new_float(0)` | `array.new<float>(0)` |
| Manuel EMA hesaplama | `ta.ema(close, len)` |

